clinical_study.brief_title: Dose Ranging Study - Macroflux Parathyroid Hormone (PTH) in Postmenopausal Women With Osteoporosis
clinical_study.official_title: A Dose Ranging Study of the Effects of Macroflux® PTH Compared With Macroflux® Placebo and FORTEO® in Postmenopausal Women With Osteoporosis

brief_summary.textblock: A Multi-center study to determine effects of various doses of Macroflux Parathryroid Hormone (PTH) in women with osteoporosis

study_design_info.masking: Quadruple (Participant, Care Provider, Investigator, Outcomes Assessor)
